{"questionId":"17482","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Let <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"X\">\n  <mi>X</mi>\n</math></span> and <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"Y\">\n  <mi>Y</mi>\n</math></span> be normally distributed with&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"X \\sim {\\text{N}}\\left( {14{\\text{, }}{a^2}} \\right)\">\n  <mi>X</mi>\n  <mo>∼</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>N</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>14</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>,&nbsp;</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>a</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span> and&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"Y \\sim {\\text{N}}\\left( {22{\\text{, }}{a^2}} \\right)\">\n  <mi>Y</mi>\n  <mo>∼</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>N</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>22</mn>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>,&nbsp;</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <msup>\n          <mi>a</mi>\n          <mn>2</mn>\n        </msup>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>,&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a > 0\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>&gt;</mo>\n  <mn>0</mn>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>Find <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b\"> <mi>b</mi> </math></span> so that&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"{\\text{P}}\\left( {X > b} \\right) = {\\text{P}}\\left( {Y < b} \\right)\"> <mrow> <mtext>P</mtext> </mrow> <mrow> <mo>(</mo> <mrow> <mi>X</mi> <mo>&gt;</mo> <mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mo>)</mo> </mrow> <mo>=</mo> <mrow> <mtext>P</m